For user_time_zone, user_protected, and user_contributors_enabled, these could be eliminated since they are all missing values. For user_following, it is just a variable indicating whether the scrapper is following to the tweet creator, it is also nonsensical for our generalized study.

In [12]:
db2=db.drop(columns=["user_time_zone","user_protected","user_contributors_enabled","user_following"])
